  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK663">
<l>kaṭaikoṭkac ceytakka tāṇmai yiṭaikkoṭki </l>
<l>ṉeṟṟā viḻuman tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So to perform an act as to publish it (only) at its termination is (true) manliness; for to announce it beforehand, will cause irremediable sorrow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
